---
title: Brussels Sprout Crumble with Mushrooms, Parmesan Breadcrumbs and Hazelnuts
description: A creamy mixture of Brussels sprouts, mushrooms, and Parmesan is offset by tangy champagne mustard and crunchy hazelnuts. Served over a bed of hearty brown rice, this dish is both comforting and wholesome.
